10:33.320 --> 10:35.940
 by which mating advantage could occur.

10:35.940 --> 10:38.900
 One is intra-sexual competition

10:38.900 --> 10:43.300
 with the stereotyping two stags locking horns in combat

10:43.300 --> 10:45.460
