1:37:57.660 --> 1:38:00.180
 Yeah, and I think that the circumstances

1:38:00.180 --> 1:38:02.500
 are often a mate value discrepancy

1:38:02.500 --> 1:38:06.420
 where the guy realizes correctly

1:38:06.420 --> 1:38:09.220
